{"tid":499354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"音質對耳機既重要性","createTime":"2017-12-14T16:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T15:12:20.000Z","uid":108425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6766928c38c5ed64b3472cbe19b687f429150c53","tid":499354,"uid":108425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:42:52.000Z","msg":"你地覺得音質對於選擇重唔重要 而家好多耳機都已經係藍芽 而beats 呢種不以音質為重既品牌亦興起 大家認為選耳機最重要既因素係咩？"},{"pid":"3ceff1f9eb1d23fdaa5f6d8b97adce9bf180efc3","tid":499354,"uid":75768,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"其實藍牙音質有好中分別咩"},{"pid":"ff38ae5b4d2cf263e9a378d9d891a0513f278647","tid":499354,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實藍牙音質有好大分別咩</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7a0e3b78bcf83d14e7de45e43d57adc7f4353f39","tid":499354,"uid":98551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地覺得音質對於選擇重唔重要 而家好多耳機都已經係藍芽 而beats 呢種不以音質為重既品牌亦興起 大家認為選耳機最重要既因素係咩？</blockquote><br />\n每個人選擇都唔同<br />\n有人方便行先<br />\n有人音質行先<br />\n但隨住無線技術越來越成熟<br />\n越多普通用家轉投無線"},{"pid":"668adc0040f1f78ac1bbc22bb9649d78720e857e","tid":499354,"uid":98551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實藍牙音質有好中分別咩</blockquote><br />\n睇下你用邊對耳機做比較啦<br />\n好既藍牙同差既有線比咪無乜分別"},{"pid":"4418daffece73819c633bf7d36b5cfd7dd57b91c","tid":499354,"uid":41846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:53:57.000Z","msg":"睇人嘅啫<br />\n追人聲同音色果啲<br />\n唔會介紹帶耳擴 player出街"},{"pid":"9f3e0d41fc9c4a8453ed8ba480803bd83f272430","tid":499354,"uid":151026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:12:20.000Z","msg":"第一就睇調音 之後再睇音場同分析力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}